data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own a huge home on a corner lot in the highly desirable Middle Sound Loop area. Quick access to schools, Wrightsville Beach, Intracoastal waterway, shopping and entertainment. This custom home boasts an open kitchen and living space with tons of natural light, high ceilings, and many windows (with custom blinds). The kitchen has a brand-new stove, granite counter tops, a spacious island with sink and seating, double oven, custom cabinets and tile. Enjoy your meals in the dining area or the breakfast nook. Enter from the garage to a convenient mud room area and closed off laundry room with utility sink. Relax in the living room that is pre-wired for flat screen television and has a cozy gas fireplace. The first floor has three bedrooms, two full bathrooms as well as a powder room in the front hallway. The primary bedroom has a lovely tray ceiling and ensuite primary bathroom with relaxing soaking tub, double vanity, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Tons of closet space throughout. The second floor is fully carpeted, has a landing space, a full bedroom, a full bathroom and a spacious FROG and access to attic storage.  A two-car garage and fence around the sides and back of the home provide plenty of privacy. Home is on a cul-de-sac and backs up to a natural wooded area.
